  "detailed_description": "<h1>Review Highlight</h1><p><i>In conclusion, Petey Pedro's Unbeetable Adventure is a gem of a game. Whether you're a casual gamer or looking for a family-friendly experience, this game delivers unbeetable joy, laughter, and positive vibes. I wholeheartedly recommend it to anyone looking for a delightful escape into a world of whimsy and charm.<br><br><strong>-ALEDream</strong></i></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MORE WORLDS        |    NEW MECHANICS      |    NEW POWER UPS</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>NEW VEHICLES      |     NEW BOSS FIGHTS |    MANY MORE SURPRISE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong> Help Petey Pedro get back home after falling into a magical world where the SWEETS he chose over a healthy beet are now his worst nightmare.</strong></i> <i><strong>A nostalgic game for those RAD 80's and 90's kids.  Easy to pick up, hard to master play style. </strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636200/extras/833f0c316aa8136cda7d441fe74cd9be.avif?t=1763335749\" width=657 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 60 Levels to BEET and master. Hand crafter themed pixel graphic levels each with a unique soundtrack.  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636200/extras/e6d88242edd3b7b29031c84bfd36cfd2.poster.avif?t=1763335749\" width=960 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636200/extras/e6d88242edd3b7b29031c84bfd36cfd2.webm?t=1763335749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636200/extras/e6d88242edd3b7b29031c84bfd36cfd2.mp4?t=1763335749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636200/extras/19310a50e70ad2ffb64702e2e579b0f3.avif?t=1763335749\" width=657 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Know every nook and cranny? Try BEETing the SPEED RECORD in every level.  Could there be an ability that helps you?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636200/extras/36dc2a6e8d0aa5b58999ac4d869816cb.poster.avif?t=1763335749\" width=960 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636200/extras/36dc2a6e8d0aa5b58999ac4d869816cb.webm?t=1763335749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636200/extras/36dc2a6e8d0aa5b58999ac4d869816cb.mp4?t=1763335749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636200/extras/b49684a26edc80d83abbcc2924ddb541.avif?t=1763335749\" width=657 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636200/extras/198cf8ade5b8978bda0751bb550eebb2.poster.avif?t=1763335749\" width=960 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636200/extras/198cf8ade5b8978bda0751bb550eebb2.webm?t=1763335749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636200/extras/198cf8ade5b8978bda0751bb550eebb2.mp4?t=1763335749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*Collect coins to upgrade your <strong>GLASSES</strong> giving you <strong>VISION POWER</strong> with new <strong>SKILLS (This creates an organic difficulty level such as certain abilities could make the game play easier or harder)</strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*Collect Hidden Magical Eggs</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*<strong>GET the Speed Runner Glasses to BEET the record for each level.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636200/extras/6d5f5fc87915b9f71735044d610c147a.avif?t=1763335749\" width=657 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every world has a puzzle stage to find.  Your <strong><u>KEY</u></strong> to finding these are your observation skills.  Can you find them all?  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636200/extras/dba0686d32962902ad4cbeeeace83a4b.poster.avif?t=1763335749\" width=960 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636200/extras/dba0686d32962902ad4cbeeeace83a4b.webm?t=1763335749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636200/extras/dba0686d32962902ad4cbeeeace83a4b.mp4?t=1763335749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>[h1]<strong><u>NEW BOSS FIGHTS!</u></strong>[/h1]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636200/extras/7bcaa3e2bf66bac953245459acb75842.poster.avif?t=1763335749\" width=960 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636200/extras/7bcaa3e2bf66bac953245459acb75842.webm?t=1763335749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636200/extras/7bcaa3e2bf66bac953245459acb75842.mp4?t=1763335749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <strong><i>PLUS MANY MORE NEW ADDITIONS.  DOWNLOAD THE UPDATED PETEY PEDRO UNBEETABLE ADVENTURE GAME</i></strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Warning: Game contains colorful imagery that may be harmful to players with photosensitive epilepsy or similar condition. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
